OL,3,CHundreds of tower block residents told
OL,4,Cto move out for three years
OL,6,FHundreds of residents of two aging
OL,7,Ftower blocks say they are "devastated"
OL,8,Fat being asked to move out of their
OL,9,Fhomes for up to three years.
OL,11,FSocial landlord Together Housing says
OL,12,F"substantial" and "extensive"
OL,13,Fstructural work is needed on St James'
OL,14,FCourt and Albion Court flats in
OL,15,FHalifax town centre - and that
OL,16,Fhundreds of residents will have to
OL,17,Fleave in order for it to be carried
OL,18,Fout.
