OL,3,CHundreds of tower block residents told
OL,4,Cto move out for three years
OL,6,FSome people have lived in the blocks
OL,7,Ffor decades, including 75-year-old
OL,8,FRichard Guillot.
OL,10,F"This has been my home for 22 years,
OL,11,FI've made it my home, I've put
OL,12,Fpictures up of the family, and I've
OL,13,Fmade it as comfortable as I can," said
OL,14,FMr Guillot.
OL,16,F"I've been quite happy living here."
OL,18,FMr Guillot said he is "absolutely
OL,19,Fmortified" at the prospect of being
OL,20,Fmade to leave.
