OL,3,CHundreds of tower block residents told
OL,4,Cto move out for three years
OL,6,FRolling repairs to St James' Court and
OL,7,FAlbion Court have been carried out for
OL,8,Fyears, but now Together Homes says
OL,9,F"substantial work" taking up to three
OL,10,Fyears is needed to bring them up to
OL,11,Fscratch.
OL,13,FA total of 130 households have been
OL,14,Fgiven 18 months to leave.
OL,16,F"(I'm) devastated, I thought I'd be
OL,17,Fhere until I die," said one woman.
OL,19,F"I don't know where I'm going to go,
OL,20,Fwhere are they going to house us?"
