OL,6,FAnother said it was like the "end of
OL,7,Fan era".
OL,9,F"We're not sure whether they're going
OL,10,Fto drop them or refurb them," she said.
OL,12,F"It's just sad, it's like a little
OL,13,Fcommunity."
OL,15,FTogether Housing's executive director
OL,16,Fof operations, Michelle Allott, said
OL,17,Fthe decision had been "really
OL,18,Fdifficult".
