OL,3,CHundreds of tower block residents told
OL,4,Cto move out for three years
OL,6,F"Nobody ever wants to ask people to
OL,7,Fleave their homes, it's a really
OL,8,Fdifficult decision, but the life of
OL,9,Fthe properties has come to that
OL,10,Fnatural end where we need to do some
OL,11,Fmajor works, and that decision hasn't
OL,12,Fbeen taken lightly," she said.
OL,14,F"It's really important to make the
OL,15,Fright decision, but the right decision
OL,16,Fis to move people out."
OL,18,FTogether Housing has offered money to
OL,19,Fresidents to move out, but on the
OL,20,Fcondition that they cannot then move
OL,21,Fback in once the work is done.
