OL,3,CHundreds of tower block residents told
OL,4,Cto move out for three years
OL,6,FDawn Oliver has lived in one of the
OL,7,Fblocks since 2019, and believed she
OL,8,Fwould see out her days there.
OL,10,F"I don't know (what to do) when 18
OL,11,Fmonths comes up, I don't know," she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"Can they just kick us out? I don't
OL,15,Fknow. They've offered us money, but
OL,16,Fit's not about the money, it's about
OL,17,Fthe friendships that we've got here,
OL,18,Fand everything else."
OL,20,FTogether Homes said it has offered to
OL,21,Fhelp find people a new place to live.
